OL,3,CBin strikes, potholes and the Middle
OL,4,CEast: What's driving Birmingham voters
OL,6,FThe ongoing bin strike, crumbling
OL,7,Froads and even international conflict
OL,8,Fare shaping how people in Birmingham
OL,9,Fplan to vote in next month's local
OL,10,Felections, according to a new ITV News
OL,11,FCentral poll.
OL,13,FThe survey of 871 residents suggests
OL,14,Flocal frustrations are dominating the
OL,15,Fpolitical agenda in the UK's second
OL,16,Fcity - with the bin dispute emerging
OL,17,Fas the single biggest issue facing
OL,18,Fvoters.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
