OL,3,CBin strikes, potholes and the Middle
OL,4,CEast: What's driving Birmingham voters
OL,6,FAlmost six in ten people (59%) said
OL,7,Fresolving the strike is one of their
OL,8,Ftop priorities, and almost two-thirds
OL,9,F(63%) said it will directly influence
OL,10,Fhow they vote.
OL,12,FThe findings underline just how
OL,13,Fcentral the row over waste collection
OL,14,Fhas become, with more than half of
OL,15,Fvoters (51%) saying they oppose the
OL,16,Fway the council has handled the
OL,17,Fdispute.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
