CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776435066
OL,3,CBin strikes, potholes and the Middle
OL,4,CEast: What's driving Birmingham voters
OL,6,FPotholes and road repairs rank as the
OL,7,Fsecond biggest concern, with 44% of
OL,8,Fresidents placing it among their top
OL,9,Fissues, followed by housing and
OL,10,Fhomelessness at 40%.
OL,12,FThere are also wider concerns about
OL,13,Fday-to-day life in the city - from
OL,14,Fcouncil tax levels to education and
OL,15,Fantisocial behaviour - all
OL,16,Fcontributing to a sense that basic
OL,17,Fservices are under strain.
OL,19,FThat frustration is reflected in
OL,20,Fpublic confidence.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776435066
OL,3,CBin strikes, potholes and the Middle
OL,4,CEast: What's driving Birmingham voters
OL,6,FMore than half of residents (55%)
OL,7,Fbelieve Birmingham is heading in the
OL,8,Fwrong direction, while nearly three
OL,9,Fquarters (73%) said they lack
OL,10,Fconfidence in the council to deliver
OL,11,Fbasic services reliably.
OL,13,FAlmost two-thirds (65%) also said they
OL,14,Fare getting poor value for money.
OL,16,FBut while local issues dominate,
OL,17,Fglobal events are still cutting
OL,18,Fthrough.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
