PN,37606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776435066
OL,3,CBin strikes, potholes and the Middle
OL,4,CEast: What's driving Birmingham voters
OL,6,FMore than a quarter of voters (27%)
OL,7,Fsaid the conflict in the Middle East
OL,8,Fwill affect how they vote, a sign that
OL,9,Finternational issues are also
OL,10,Finfluencing political attitudes at a
OL,11,Flocal level.
OL,13,FThe poll paints a picture of an
OL,14,Felectorate pulled in multiple
OL,15,Fdirections, frustrated by everyday
OL,16,Fproblems, sceptical about leadership,
OL,17,Fand influenced by events far beyond
OL,18,Fthe city.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
