OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1776435066
OL,3,CBin strikes, potholes and the Middle
OL,4,CEast: What's driving Birmingham voters
OL,6,FWith no single issue defining the
OL,7,Frace, and no clear political
OL,8,Ffrontrunner, the result could hinge on
OL,9,Fwhich party voters trust most to fix
OL,10,Fthe basics - while navigating wider
OL,11,Fpressures at home and abroad.
OL,13,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,14,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,15,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,16,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/7
